data.description: Welcome to this beautiful move in ready residence located in the gated community of Carriage Gate Plantation in Brunswick, GA. This meticulously crafted 2215 sq ft home, built by Maritime builders, offers an exceptional living experience with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and a range of modern amenities. The home boasts an inviting open floor plan, accentuated by ample natural light and a seamless flow between spaces. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring all brand new stainless-steel appliances, sleek Quartz counter-tops, and plenty of abundant cabinet space. The luxurious master bathroom is equipped with double vanities and a dual walk-in closet unlike any, that wraps around the back half of the bathroom, providing ample storage and comfort. This home has a laundry room with plenty of space and a new LG Washer and dryer that goes with the property.  Residents enjoy access to the community pool, offering a perfect spot for relaxation and leisure. The home is fitted with contemporary fixtures, ensuring convenience and comfort for everyday living. Owners would consider selling this home furnished.  This desirable neighborhood is ideally situated, being 6 miles from the Brunswick-Golden Isles Airport, 7 miles from FLETC (Federal Law Enforcement Training Centers), and a mere 9 miles from the main shopping centers in Brunswick, GA. Residents benefit from easy access to major transportation routes and proximity to various amenities. Carriage Gate Plantation is known for its great neighborhood feel, offering a secure and family-friendly environment. It's a welcoming community that fosters a sense of belonging while providing convenient access to nearby facilities, including schools, shopping centers, and entertainment venues. This splendid home epitomizes modern living with its thoughtful design, convenient location.  Experience the comfort and convenience this property has to offer in one of Brunswick's most sought-after neighborhoods.
